text: Ocugen #NASDAQ: $OCGN, its partner, Bharat #Biotech, released data from its Phase 3 trial of #COVID19 #vaccine, Covaxin. The vaccine had efficacy in mild & moderate COVID-19 disease of 78% with efficacy against severe COVID-19 disease of 100%. It closed the week up 67% to $9.63. https://t.co/SlkKy8gXNS
